app_name: Journal X My Diary with Lock
release_note: BUG FIXES 1. iPhone X scroll issue: the writing screen was not scrolling as the user is typing. It s now fixed. 2. Search screen being unresponsive: when the user taps on any entry in search screen that entry doesn t open up. It s now fixed. 3. Facebook sign up not working: sign up using facebook caused some issues. It s fixed 4. The smoothness of writing screen: user can now scroll through already written text without needing to dismiss keypad. 5. IAP price per localization: instead of just USD IAP price will be now displayed in your local currency selected in iPhone settings. 6. Headline saving issue: the headline was not saving as the user types. It s now fixed. 7. Photos album contains favorite albums too. 8. Buttons mixing with a status bar in iPhone X: sometimes the buttons of writing screen gets mixed with the status bar when keypad is dismissed. It s now fixed. 9. Entry saving issue: sometimes when the user only adds and delete certain elements in the entry except for text that entry doesn t get save. It s now fixed. 10. Typo: there were some typoes in the app for words like stickers reminder etc. They all are corrected. 11. Unresponsive buttons of full screen pop ups: Since the buttons of full screen pop ups were mixed with the status bar they were unresponsive. All these issues are fixed: If you find any other issues or crashes or have suggestions for our app please send them to journalapp9 gmail.com Thanks to all our users who reported these bugs and issues in our app. We hope to create the best journaling experience possible with your help. Thanks to all our current users to stay loyal to our app and using it for their day to day life. Journal X is now 1 year old and it s still changing and evolving all because of our customer s love and support. Thank you all again : Amogh

app_name: Journal X My Diary with Lock
release_note: CRASH FIXES: Sign up using Facebook was creating a crash. Now fixed! BUG FIX: Occasionally the in app purchase was not successful despite successful payment. Now fixed! NEW DESIGN All your entries are presented on the center screen. Swipe right to access the navigation menu and swipe left to view the calendar. From launch screen to color scheme everything is improved! Table rows height has been decreased to fit a greater number of entries. New stickers and avatar have been added. We will launch a new version with iPad support too in the coming month. NEW FEATURES 1. Invisible Mode paid users only : Hide what you re writing from people sitting around you. 2. Calendar: All your entries dates are shown in a calendar for a better understanding. 3. Journal X Pro Mini: Pay a fixed price to use all the Journal X Pro features expect cloud storage for just 9.99 4.99 MAJOR CHANGES 1. Stickers feature is now a paid feature. 2. Journal X Pro is more affordable at 50 off offer 9.99 year only. 3. Real time syncing can be done manually too also by pull down to refresh.
